data.name: story.Text
data.value:
You are a young apprentice wizard who has been given a quest to prove that he is of age to become a fully-fledged wizard. Your journey will be long and you must face a creature - the evil Makhana - a squid-like creature that is half machine and half brain.
Makhana has plagued the people of your home village for many years. In order for you, the apprentice, to defeat him, you must first battle four of his minions: Cocoon, Peruna, Floppit and Fluppit.
Only then, can you finally come of age and be the wizard that you rightfully deserve.
